'''海风'''是一杯由[[伏特加|伏特加]]、蔓越莓汁和西柚汁制成并且经常在夏日饮用的鸡尾酒，<ref name="stillspirits">{{Cite web | title = Seabreeze - Cocktails - Flavour Essences | url = http://stillspirits.com/au/flavour-essences/cocktails/seabreeze.html | publisher = Still Spirits | accessdate = 13 June 2011 |  archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110828023918/http://stillspirits.com/au/flavour-essences/cocktails/seabreeze.html | archivedate = 28 August 2011 }}</ref>海风也可以加入调酒壶里摇动以使酒体上部出现泡沫。<ref name="stillspirits"/>它同时是一杯IBA官方鸡尾酒。<ref name="stillspirits"/>

这款饮料遵循传统的鸡尾酒构造法则，即平衡强烈的（[[酒精|酒精]]）和弱的（[[果汁|果汁]]）以及甜度和酸度的关系。<ref name="stillspirits"/><ref name="eatoutzone">{{cite web | author=Eatoutzone | title=Cocktails with Vodka | url=http://www.eatoutzone.com/Cocktail_with_Vodka.htm#Sea_Breeze | accessdate=2007-11-08 | dead-url=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704065346/http://www.eatoutzone.com/Cocktail_with_Vodka.htm#Sea_Breeze | archivedate=2008-07-04  }}</ref>

湾（海湾）风或夏威夷海风，除了用菠萝汁代替西柚汁外，其余与海风制作方法一样。<ref name="eatoutzone"/><ref name="Agencies2000">{{cite book|author=Harvard Student Agencies|title=The official Harvard Student Agencies bartending course|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4iY21z80I0QC&pg=PA47|accessdate=2011-06-13|date=2000-01-15|publisher=Macmillan|isbn=978-0-312-25286-1|page=47|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720104525/https://books.google.com/books?id=4iY21z80I0QC&pg=PA47|dead-url=no}}</ref> 它与{{le|科德角 (鸡尾酒)|Cape Codder (cocktail)|科德角}}（缺少柚子汁）和{{le|鹹狗|Salty dog (cocktail)}}（缺少蔓越莓汁，有盐霜边缘）也有密切关系。<ref name="DeGroff2008">{{cite book|author=Dale DeGroff|title=The Essential Cocktail: The Art of Mixing Perfect Drinks|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QQPQnCwBdJ8C&pg=PT332|accessdate=2011-06-13|date=2008-10-28|publisher=Random House Digital, Inc.|isbn=978-0-307-40573-9|page=332|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804141019/https://books.google.com/books?id=QQPQnCwBdJ8C&pg=PT332|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
这款鸡尾酒诞生于20世纪20年代末，但最初配方与今天配方不同，因为最初的“海风”中使用的是[[金酒|金酒]]和[[红石榴糖浆|红石榴糖浆]]，<ref>{{cite web | author=Cocktail Idea | title=Sea breeze cocktail recipe | url=http://cocktail.idea.hu/sea-breeze | accessdate=2007-11-08 | dead-url=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071021010919/http://cocktail.idea.hu/sea-breeze | archivedate=2007-10-21  }}</ref>并且当时正值禁酒时代接近尾声。在20世纪30年代，海风的配方是金酒、{{le|杏子白兰地|Apricot brandy}}、红石榴糖浆和柠檬汁。<ref name="Calabrese2006">{{cite book|author=Salvatore Calabrese|title=Classic Cocktails|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ec7-H6oHpe4C&pg=PA158|accessdate=2011-05-23|date=2006-04-28|publisher=Sterling Publishing Company, Inc.|isbn=978-1-4027-3910-1|pages=158–|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721042558/https://books.google.com/books?id=ec7-H6oHpe4C&pg=PA158|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来，海风的配方会包含伏特加、[[干苦艾酒|干苦艾酒]]、[[加利安奴|加利安奴力娇酒]]和[[庫拉索酒|蓝库拉索力娇酒]]。<ref name="Calabrese2006"/>

20世纪30年代的蔓越莓种植者合作社发展成了{{le|优鲜沛|Ocean Spray (cooperative)}}（Ocean Spray），50年代时它们将蔓越莓汁推向市场。<ref name="DeGroff2008"/>于是蔓越莓汁开始与酒精混合在一起，先是与金酒混合，后来又与伏特加混合。<ref name="DeGroff2008"/>诞生了后来被称为科德角的鸡尾酒，后来又陆续创造了灰狗、咸狗、湾风、海风等后代产品<ref name="DeGroff2008"/>，从20世纪60年代开始，这类鸡尾酒开始零星的出现在最受欢迎的十大混合饮料中。<ref name="DeGroff2008"/>

根据一些人的说法，“海风”、“科德角”和“湾风”直到20世纪70年代才变得非常流行。<ref name="CharmingBourgoin2009">{{cite book|author1=Cheryl Charming|author2=Susan Bourgoin|title=Knack Bartending Basics: More Than 400 Classic and Contemporary Cocktails for Any Occasion|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AJKr67ceXpMC&pg=PA123|accessdate=2011-06-13|date=2009-06-02|publisher=Globe Pequot|isbn=978-1-59921-504-4|pages=123|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914194720/https://books.google.com/books?id=AJKr67ceXpMC&pg=PA123|dead-url=no}}</ref>这是因为在1959年，美国卫生部指出蔓越莓作物受到有毒除草剂的污染，使得蔓越莓产业重受打击。<ref name="CharmingBourgoin2009"/>

